name: m4
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.4.17" %}

package:
    name: m4
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: m4-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/m4/m4-{{ version }}.tar.gz

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]

test:
    commands:
        - m4 --help
        - m4 --version

about:
    home: http://www.gnu.org/software/m4/
    license: GPL3
    summary: Implementation of the traditional Unix macro processor.

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
